metadata.name: NFTHATEBOT
metadata.description: 机器人滚出去,这只是一个游戏,付费的用户将会优先开启approve权限,free用户将于72小时以后开启,销售完成后24小时内,所有盲盒开启,当你打开得到一张1ETH的彩票,你会得到1WETH的offer,甚至是一个空投到你钱包的NFT.记住,OFFER只生效24小时,免费只是免费.记住,不一定能卖完,不一定能卖完,不一定能卖完.Get out of the robot, this is just a game, paid users will give priority to open the approve permission, free users will open after 72 hours, within 24 hours after the sale is completed, all blind boxes will be opened, when you open it to get 1ETH, you will get 1WETH offer, or even an NFT airdropped to your wallet. Remember, OFFER is only valid for 24 hours, and free is just free.
